      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is a well-maintained E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings, preserving the iconic 50/50 weight distribution and precise steering rack feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical synchronization of the valvetrain and the linear throttle response make this a superlative driver's specimen.",
